=== Name-Based Starting Gold ===
Certain character names result in different starting gold amounts.

'''How It Works:'''
* The name is converted to numeric values
* Calculation determines gold
* Some names give bonus gold

'''Example Names:'''
* Various names result in 120+ gold instead of standard amount

